減された場合、屈折の罠はその点数に等しい点数のダメージを、そのクリーチャーやプレイヤーに与える。','Se um oponente conjurar uma mágica instantânea ou um feitiço vermelho neste turno, você poderá pagar {W} em vez de pagar o custo de mana de Armadilha de Refração.£Previna os próximos 3 pontos de dano que seriam causados por uma fonte de sua escolha a você e/ou a permanentes sob seu controle neste turno Se o dano for prevenido desta maneira, Armadilha de Refração causará uma quantidade equivalente de dano à criatura ou ao jogador alvo.','Если оппонент разыграл красное мгновенное заклинание или заклинание волшебства в этом ходу, вы можете заплатить {W} вместо уплаты мана-стоимости Западни Преломления.£Предотвратите следующие 3 повреждения, которые выбранный вами источник должен нанести вам и #_(или)_# перманентам под вашим контролем в этом ходу. Если повреждения предотвращаются таким образом, Западня Преломления наносит столько же повреждений целевому существу или игроку.','Si un oponente lanza un hechizo instantáneo o conjuro rojo este turno, puedes pagar {W} en lugar de pagar el coste de maná de la Trampa de refracción.£Prevén los siguientes 3 puntos de daño que una fuente de tu elección fuera a hacerte a ti y/o a permanentes que controlas este turno. Si se previene daño de esta manera, la Trampa de refracción hace esa misma cantidad de daño a la criatura o jugador objetivo.','If an opponent cast a red instant or sorcery spell this turn, you may pay {W} rather than pay Refraction Trap''s mana cost.£The next 3 damage that a source of your choice would deal to you or a permanent you control this turn is dealt to target creature or player instead.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('189180','Rest for the Weary','WWK','Instant','C','{1}{W}','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Target player gains 4 life.£#_Landfall_# — If you had a land enter the battlefield under your control this turn, that player gains 8 life instead.','#_Zendikar is a brutal taskmaster, but sometimes it offers unexpected solace._#',NULL,'James Paick','18','3.636','£3/1/2010: Whether you had a land enter the battlefield under your control this turn is checked as this spell resolves, not as you cast it.£3/1/2010: Having more than one land enter the battlefield under your control this turn provides no additional benefit.£3/1/2010: The landfall ability checks for an action that has happened in the past. It doesn’t matter if a land that entered the battlefield under your control previously in the turn is still on the battlefield, is still under your control, or is still a land.£3/1/2010: Once the spell resolves, having a land enter the battlefield under your control provides no further benefit.£3/1/2010: The effect of this spell’s landfall ability replaces its normal effect. If you had a land enter the battlefield under your control this turn, only the landfall-based effect happens.','W',NULL,'0.09','0.28','1.43',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'W','疲惫歇息',NULL,'Du repos pour les misérables','Ruhe für die Erschöpften','Riposo per gli Esausti','疲弊の休息','Repouso dos Cansados','Покой для Утомленных','Descanso para los agotados','Rest for the Weary','瞬间',NULL,'Éphémère','Spontanzauber','Istantaneo','インスタント','Mágica Instantânea','Мгновенное заклинание','Instantáneo','Instant','目标牌手获得4点生命。£地落～如果本回合中有地在你的操控下进战场，则改为该牌手获得8点生命。',NULL,'Le joueur ciblé gagne 4 points de vie.£Toucheterre — Si vous avez fait arriver un terrain sur le champ de bataille sous votre contrôle ce tour-ci, ce joueur gagne 8 points de vie à la place.','Ein Spieler deiner Wahl erhält 4 Lebenspunkte dazu.£Landung — Falls ein Land unter deiner Kontrolle in diesem Zug ins Spiel gekommen ist, erhält dieser Spieler stattdessen 8 Lebenspunkte dazu.','Un giocatore bersaglio guadagna 4 punti vita.£Terraferma — Se hai fatto entrare nel campo di battaglia una terra sotto il tuo controllo in questo turno, quel giocatore guadagna invece 8 punti vita.','プレイヤー１人を対象とする。そのプレイヤーは４点のライフを得る。£上陸 ― このターン、あなたのコントロール下で土地が戦場に出ている場合、代わりにそのプレイヤーは８点のライフを得る。','O jogador alvo ganha 4 pontos de vida.£Aterragem — Se você teve um terreno que entrou no campo de batalha sob o seu controle neste turno, em vez disso, aquele jogador ganha 8 pontos de vida.','Целевой игрок получает 4 жизни.£Землепад — Если земля вышла на поле битвы под вашим контролем в этом ходу, тот игрок получает 8 жизней вместо этого.','El jugador objetivo gana 4 vidas.£Aterrizaje — Si una tierra entró al campo de batalla bajo tu control este turno, en vez de eso, ese jugador gana 8 vidas.','Target player gains 4 life.£Landfall - If you had a land enter the battlefield under your control this turn, that player gains 8 life instead.','#_赞迪卡好似凶蛮的工头，但它有时也会提供意外的抚慰。_#',NULL,'#_Zendikar est une maîtresse brutale, mais elle offre parfois un réconfort inespéré._#','#_Zendikar ist wie ein brutaler Zuchtmeister, doch unerwartet findet man manchmal auch ein wenig Trost._#','#_Zendikar è un brutale aguzzino, ma a volte offre insperate consolazioni._#','#_ゼンディカーは残酷な長であるが、時に予想外の癒しを与えてくれることもある。_#','#_Zendikar é um capataz cruel, mas às vezes oferece um consolo inesperado._#','#_Зендикар не ведает жалости, но иногда предлагает неожиданное облегчение._#','#_Zendikar es un capataz brutal, pero a veces ofrece un descanso inesperado._#','#_Zendikar is a brutal taskmaster, but sometimes she offers unexpected solace._#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('191549','Ricochet Trap','WWK','Instant — Trap','U','{3}{R}','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'If an opponent cast a blue spell this turn, you may pay {R} rather than pay this spell''s mana cost.£Change the target of target spell with a single target.','#_In his last seconds, Remhas regretted using his most powerful spell._#',NULL,'Jaime Jones','87','3.824','£3/1/2010: If you cast Ricochet Trap for {R}, you don’t have to target the blue spell an opponent cast.£3/1/2010: Ricochet Trap targets only the spell whose target will be changed. It doesn’t directly affect the original target of that spell or the new target of that spell.£3/1/2010: You don’t choose the new target for the spell until Ricochet Trap resolves. You must change the target if possible. However, you can’t change the target to an illegal target. If there are no legal targets to choose from, the target isn’t changed. It doesn’t matter if the original target of that spell has somehow become illegal itself.£3/1/2010: If you cast Ricochet Trap targeting a spell that targets a spell on the stack (like Cancel does, for example), you can’t change that spell’s target to itself. You can, however, change that spell’s target to Ricochet Trap. If you do, that spell won’t resolve when it tries to resolve because Ricochet Trap will have left the stack by then.£3/1/2010: If a spell targets multiple things, you can’t target it with Ricochet Trap, even if all but one of those targets have become illegal.£3/1/2010: If a spell targets the same player or object multiple times, you can’t target it with Ricochet Trap.','R',NULL,'0.29','0.61','1.9',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'R','跳弹陷阱',NULL,'Piège à ricochet','Querschläger-Falle','Trappola a Rimbalzo','跳ね返りの罠','Armadilha de Ricochete','Западня с Рикошетом','Trampa de rebote','Ricochet Trap','瞬间～陷阱',NULL,'Éphémère : piège','Spontanzauber — Falle','Istantaneo — Trappola','インスタント ― 罠','Mágica Instantânea — Armadilha','Мгновенное заклинание — Ловушка','Instantáneo — Trampa','Instant — Trap','如果本回合中某对手施放蓝色咒语，你可以支付{R}，而不支付跳弹陷阱的法术力费用。£为仅指定单一目标的目标咒语更改目标。',NULL,'Si un adversaire a lancé un sort bleu ce tour-ci, vous pouvez payer {R} à la place du coût de mana du Piège à ricochet.£Remplacez la cible du sort ciblé qui a une cible unique.','Falls ein Gegner in diesem Zug einen blauen Zauberspruch gewirkt hat, kannst du {R} bezahlen, anstatt die Manakosten der Querschläger-Falle zu bezahlen.£Verändere das Ziel eines Zauberspruchs deiner Wahl, der nur ein einzelnes Ziel hat.','Se un avversario ha lanciato una magia blu in questo turno, puoi pagare {R} invece di pagare il costo di ma